<plot>Correre contro is the story of a friendship between Pablo and Daniele. Pablo is a paraplegic who works at a rehabilitation center with more seriously injured patients. Daniele is sent there to do community service because he is a conscientious objector. At first they don't get along but a friendship develops that is soon threatened by their mutual interest in a singer.</plot><url>http://localhost:8983/solr/movie.html?115908</url></doc>
